 count to run concurrently with\neach other, for a total of 5 years. SA: $3,800; No Fine;\nRestitution: $3,717.98.\nDefendant is hereby committed to the BOP for Life on Count\n1sss; 5 years on Count 2sss; 6 years on Count 3sss; 20 years on\nCounts 4ss, 5ss, 6ss, 7ss, 8ss, 9ss, 10ss, 11ss, 12ss, 13ss, 14ss,\n15ss, 16ss, 17ss, and 18ss; 8 years on Counts 19ss and 20ss; 10\nyears on Count 35ss; 15 years on Counts 36ss; 3 years on Count\n39ss; and 5 years on Count 41ss; all counts to run concurrently\nwith each other, for a total of Life. Additionally, on Counts\n21ss, 22ss, 23ss, 24ss, 25ss, 26ss, 27ss, 28ss, 29ss, 30ss, 31ss,\n18:111.F ASSAULTING/RESISTING/IMPEDING\n32ss, 33ss, and 34ss, a term of Life is imposed on each count, to\nOFFICERS/EMPLOYEES\nbe served consecutively to each other and consecutively to all\n(19ss-20ss)\nother counts, for a total term of imprisonment of Life. TSR: 5\nyears on each of Counts 1sss, 21ss, 22ss, 23ss, 24ss, 25ss, 26ss,\n27ss, 28ss, 29ss, 30ss, 31ss, 32ss, 33ss, and 34ss; 3 years on\nCounts 2sss, 3sss, 4ss, 5ss, 6ss, 7ss, 8ss, 9ss, 10ss, 11ss, 12ss,\n13ss, 14ss, 15ss, 16ss, 17ss, 18ss, 19ss, 20ss, 35ss, and 36ss;\nand 1 year on Count 39ss; each count to run concurrently with\neach other, for a total of 5 years. SA: $3,800; No Fine;\nRestitution: $3,717.98.\nVIOLENT CRIME/DRUGS/MACHINE GUN\nDismissed on Government Motion\n(21s-34s)\nDefendant is hereby committed to the BOP for Life on Count\n1sss; 5 years on Count 2sss; 6 years on Count 3sss; 20 years on\nCounts 4ss, 5ss, 6ss, 7ss, 8ss, 9ss, 10ss, 11ss, 12ss, 13ss, 14ss,\n15ss, 16ss, 17ss, and 18ss; 8 years on Counts 19ss and 20ss; 10\nyears on Count 35ss; 15 years on Counts 36ss; 3 years on Count\n39ss; and 5 years on Count 41ss; all counts to run concurrently\nwith each other, for a total of Life. Additionally, on Counts\n21ss, 22ss, 23ss, 24ss, 25ss, 26ss, 27ss, 28ss, 29ss, 30ss, 31ss,\n18:924C.F VIOLENT CRIME/DRUGS/MACHINE GUN 32ss, 33ss, and 34ss, a term of Life is imposed on each count, to\n(21ss-34ss) be served consecutively to each other and consecutively to all\nother counts, for a total term of imprisonment of Life. TSR: 5\nyears on each of Counts 1sss, 21ss, 22ss, 23ss, 24ss, 25ss, 26ss,\n27ss, 28ss, 29ss, 30ss, 31ss, 32ss, 33ss, and 34ss; 3 years on\nCounts 2sss, 3sss, 4ss, 5ss, 6ss, 7ss, 8ss, 9ss, 10ss, 11ss, 12ss,\n13ss, 14ss, 15ss, 16ss, 17ss, 18ss, 19ss, 20ss, 35ss, and 36ss;\nand 1 year on Count 39ss; each count to run concurrently with\neach other, for a total of 5 years. SA: $3,800; No Fine;\nRestitution: $3,717.98.\nGOVERNMENT PROPERTY OR CONTRACTS > $100\nDismissed on Government Motion\n(35s)\nDefendant is hereby committed to the BOP for Life on Count\n1sss; 5 years on Count 2sss; 6 years on Count 3sss; 20 years on\nCounts 4ss, 5ss, 6ss, 7ss, 8ss, 9ss, 10ss, 11ss, 12ss, 13ss, 14ss,\n15ss, 16ss, 17ss, and 18ss; 8 years on Counts 19ss and 20ss; 10\nyears on Count 35ss; 15 years on Counts 36ss; 3 years on Count\n39ss; and 5 years on Count 41ss; all counts to run concurrently\nwith each other, for a total of Life. Additionally, on Counts\n21ss, 22ss, 23ss, 24ss, 25ss, 26ss, 27ss, 28ss, 29ss, 30ss, 31ss,\n18:1361.F GOVERNMENT PROPERTY OR CONTRACTS >\n32ss, 33ss, and 34ss, a term of Life is imposed on each count, to\n$100\nbe served consecutively to each other and consecutively to all\n(35ss)\nother counts, for a total term of imprisonment of Life. TSR: 5\nyears on each of Counts 1sss, 21ss, 22ss, 23ss, 24ss, 25ss, 26ss,\n27ss, 28ss, 29ss, 30ss, 31ss, 32ss, 33ss, and 34ss; 3 years on\nCounts 2sss, 3sss, 4ss, 5ss, 6ss, 7ss, 8ss, 9ss, 10ss, 11ss, 12ss,\n13ss, 14ss, 15ss, 16ss, 17ss, 18ss, 19ss, 20ss, 35ss, and 36ss;\nand 1 year on Count 39ss; each count to run concurrently with\neach other, for a total of 5 years. SA: $3,800; No Fine;\nRestitution: $3,717.98.\nUNLAWFUL TRANSPORT OF FIREARMS, ETC.\nDismissed on Government Motion\n(36s)\nDefendant is hereby committed to the BOP for Life on Count\n1sss; 5 years on Count 2sss; 6 years o